cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.CE, cs.DS

The paper proposes a proactive quality monitoring and control approach based on classifiers, which involves machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also discusses the impact of the choice of classifier types, selection criterion, and fusion process on the accuracy of the classifier ensemble, which falls under the scope of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SE (Software Engineering). Additionally, the paper deals with a real-world case, which suggests that it could be categorized under cs.CE (Computational Engineering) or cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
